OpenSDE News!

Structure:
	- introduced $HOME/.sde folder for global configurations
	- src/ -> tmp/ for temporal files (2006/08/01)
	- source/ folder dropped (2006/08/01)
	- Documentation -> doc/
	- misc/share/ -> etc/ (config) (2006-08-28)
	- modify the license handling to not use hardcoded licenses
	  but parse some files in etc. (2006-10-01)
Targets:
	- dropped archivista (2006/08/01)
Packages:
	- Xfce 4.4
	- gtk+ repository for generic Gtk+ applications (2006/08/03)
	  and changed those apps to use gtk+-conf.in instead of gnome's
	- gtk+ and friends to usr/ (2006-08-03)
	- php to opt/php (2006-08-06)
OpenSDE:
	- replaced old 'NEWS' file (2006/08/01)
	- updated T2 Copyright notes all around (2006/08/01)
	- introduced `sde` front-end wrapper (2006/08/20)
	- `sde commit` replaced scripts/Commit (2006/08/20)
	- CIA notifying changes on #opensde (2006-08-21)
	- Mailing lists (discussion and svn changes) (2006-09-05)
	- @opensde.org forward accounts for members (2006-09-05)

